scopecontent.p:
Files of Gray Thoron include correspondence, surveys, memoranda, applications, reports,
            announcements, and other materials pertaining to Cornell Law School admissions,
            students, curricula, and examinations; personnel recruitment information and
            applications; budgets, endowments, fundraising, scholarships, and fellowships; alumni;
            the International Legal Studies Program; academic freedom and tenure; faculty members;
            policies; and other papers relating to Thoron's position as Law School dean.
